        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "siege_weapon",
        "text": "A compact cannon that fires much smaller ammunition than typical cannons, the falconet has an undersized but lethal shot of similar weight and size to a bird of prey, hence the name. The falconet sits between the heaviest musket and traditional cannon, but its lighter size and cost make it appealing to forces that can\u2019t field a full cannon crew.",
